# Project data dirs (model files, downloads, runtime state).
# Anchored with leading `/` so this only matches the top-level data dirs and
# does NOT swallow legitimate `data/` subdirectories like
# backend/apps/catalog/data/ (catalog seed YAMLs).
/data/
/backend/data/

